  "couplingIntensity": "None",
  "description": "bodyLevel=0.95 — the body is nearly everything. bodyFreq=55Hz (A1 habitat, unwavering). filterCutoff low: the MIDI voice is filtered almost to nothing, a barely-audible ghost of melody beneath 55Hz permanence. Per OWL-II taken to its logical extreme: duophonic where the non-MIDI voice is the instrument and the MIDI voice is ornamental. Invert your conception of what you are playing. The keyboard triggers a ghost; the body is the music.",
